<!doctype html>
<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#070b16" />
    <title>Neon Ops Deck</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500;700;800&family=Rajdhani:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #070b16;
        --bg-soft: rgba(10, 16, 31, 0.86);
        --text: #eff5ff;
        --muted: #99accf;
        --cyan: #53f0ff;
        --pink: #ff4fd8;
        --amber: #ffcf53;
        --lime: #70ff9b;
        --shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html,
      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100%;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.18), transparent 28%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.18), transparent 26%),
          radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(112, 255, 155, 0.08), transparent 32%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #05070d 0%, #070b16 34%, #091223 100%);
        font-family: "Rajdhani", sans-serif;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      body::before,
      body::after {
        content: "";
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
      }

      body::before {
        background:
          linear-gradient(rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px),
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 72px 72px;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 36%, transparent 100%);
        opacity: 0.38;
        animation: grid-drift 18s linear infinite;
      }

      body::after {
        background: linear-gradient(transparent 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 48%, transparent 100%);
        background-size: 100% 4px;
        opacity: 0.18;
      }

      @keyframes grid-drift {
        from {
          transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
        }
        to {
          transform: translate3d(72px, 72px, 0);
        }
      }

      .backdrop-orb {
        position: fixed;
        width: 38rem;
        height: 38rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        filter: blur(24px);
        opacity: 0.18;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
      }

      .backdrop-orb.left {
        top: -10rem;
        left: -8rem;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.6), transparent 62%);
      }

      .backdrop-orb.right {
        right: -10rem;
        bottom: -12rem;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.7), transparent 64%);
      }

      .deck {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        width: min(1320px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 24px auto 64px;
      }

      .hero,
      .service-card,
      .workbench-card,
      .footer-card,
      .modal {
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.22);
        border-radius: 32px;
        padding: 30px;
        background:
          linear-gradient(155deg, rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.08), transparent 32%),
          linear-gradient(330deg, rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.12), transparent 40%),
          var(--bg-soft);
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      }

      .hero::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background:
          linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.1) 48%, transparent 100%);
        transform: skewX(-24deg) translateX(-120%);
        animation: scan 8s linear infinite;
      }

      @keyframes scan {
        to {
          transform: skewX(-24deg) translateX(220%);
        }
      }

      .eyebrow,
      .section-tag,
      .pill,
      .service-status,
      .button,
      .ghost-button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      }

      .eyebrow,
      .section-tag {
        border: 1px solid rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.24);
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        color: var(--cyan);
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        background: rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.08);
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .stat-grid,
      .service-grid,
      .workbench-grid,
      .footer-bar {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.45fr) minmax(280px, 0.85fr);
        align-items: end;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .headline,
      .section-header h2,
      .service-card h3,
      .workbench-card h3,
      .aside-title,
      .modal-header h3,
      .modal-body h1,
      .modal-body h2,
      .modal-body h3 {
        font-family: "Orbitron", sans-serif;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .headline {
        margin: 16px 0 12px;
        font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 8vw, 5.4rem);
        line-height: 0.9;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-shadow:
          0 0 14px rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.42),
          0 0 32px rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.26);
      }

      .headline span,
      .stat-value,
      .icon-box {
        color: var(--cyan);
      }

      .headline span {
        display: block;
      }

      .hero-copy,
      .section-header p,
      .service-card p,
      .workbench-card p,
      .aside-meta,
      .footer-card span,
      .modal-body p,
      .modal-body li {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .hero-strip {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        max-width: 48rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .hero-aside {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .pill {
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      }

      .aside-card,
      .service-card,
      .workbench-card,
      .footer-card {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 24px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        background: rgba(8, 13, 24, 0.74);
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .aside-title {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        color: var(--amber);
      }

      .aside-meta {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .stat-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      .stat {
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.16);
        background: rgba(5, 9, 18, 0.68);
      }

      .stat-value {
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
      }

      .stat-label {
        color: var(--muted);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      .section-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: end;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .section-header h2 {
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      }

      .service-grid,
      .workbench-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      }

      .service-card,
      .workbench-card {
        border-color: rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.14);
        background:
          linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04), transparent 45%),
          rgba(10, 17, 31, 0.82);
        padding: 22px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      }

      .service-card::before,
      .workbench-card::before,
      .aside-card::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .service-card::before,
      .workbench-card::before {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.12), transparent 35%, rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.09) 88%);
        opacity: 0.86;
      }

      .aside-card::after {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.18), transparent 52%);
      }

      .service-top,
      .workbench-top,
      .card-actions,
      .credential-grid {
        position: relative;
      }

      .service-top,
      .workbench-top {
        display: flex;
        align-items: start;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .icon-box {
        width: 58px;
        height: 58px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.24);
        background: rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.08);
        font-size: 1.35rem;
      }

      .service-status {
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        background: rgba(112, 255, 155, 0.12);
        color: var(--lime);
        border: 1px solid rgba(112, 255, 155, 0.18);
      }

      .service-card h3,
      .workbench-card h3 {
        position: relative;
        margin: 18px 0 10px;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      }

      .credential-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        margin: 18px 0 20px;
      }

      .credential {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        background: rgba(3, 7, 15, 0.46);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .credential span:first-child {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .credential span:last-child,
      .modal-body code {
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "Consolas", "SFMono-Regular", monospace;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .button,
      .ghost-button {
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        font-family: "Orbitron", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
      }

      .card-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .button {
        color: #031019;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), #7effd4);
        border: 1px solid rgba(126, 255, 212, 0.6);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .ghost-button {
        color: var(--text);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      }

      .button:hover,
      .ghost-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .service-note {
        position: relative;
        margin-top: 16px;
        padding-left: 14px;
        color: #d8e4ff;
        border-left: 2px solid rgba(255, 207, 83, 0.5);
      }

      .modal-shell {
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        display: none;
        place-items: center;
        background: rgba(2, 6, 14, 0.82);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
        z-index: 40;
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .modal-shell.active {
        display: grid;
      }

      .modal {
        width: min(920px, 100%);
        max-height: min(84vh, 920px);
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 28px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.18);
        background:
          linear-gradient(155deg, rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.08), transparent 38%),
          rgba(6, 11, 23, 0.95);
      }

      .modal-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 22px 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      }

      .modal-header h3 {
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      }

      .modal-body {
        overflow: auto;
        max-height: calc(84vh - 82px);
        padding: 26px 28px 30px;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .modal-body code {
        padding: 0.18rem 0.4rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.08);
      }

      .modal-body pre {
        overflow: auto;
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 16px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(83, 240, 255, 0.16);
        background: rgba(4, 8, 16, 0.88);
      }

      .modal-close {
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        color: var(--text);
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .footer-bar {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      .footer-card strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        color: var(--amber);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      }

      @media (max-width: 960px) {
        .hero-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .stat-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .deck {
          width: min(100% - 20px, 1320px);
          margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .hero,
        .service-card,
        .workbench-card {
          border-radius: 22px;
        }

        .headline {
          font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .credential {
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="backdrop-orb left"></div>
    <div class="backdrop-orb right"></div>

    <main class="deck">
      <section class="hero">
        <span class="eyebrow"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> neon operations deck</span>
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div>
            <h1 class="headline">
              LAB
              <span>OVERRUN</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-copy">
              Portale operativo unificato per repository, automazione, modelli locali e ambienti
              di sviluppo, con un server PostgreSQL dedicato al data plane dei workbench. Tutto
              passa dal gateway HTTPS del lab, con credenziali root esposte in chiaro per uso
              interno controllato.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-strip">
              <span class="pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i> endpoint: ${LAB_EXTERNAL_URL}/lab/</span>
              <span class="pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i> accesso centralizzato</span>
              <span class="pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i> storage solo su volumi</span>
              <span class="pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-satellite-dish"></i> gateway unico</span>
              <span class="pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-diagram-next"></i> dual network topology</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-grid">
              <div class="stat">
                <div class="stat-value">4</div>
                <div class="stat-label">servizi core</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat">
                <div class="stat-value">5</div>
                <div class="stat-label">ambienti dev</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat">
                <div class="stat-value">1</div>
                <div class="stat-label">gateway https</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-aside">
            <div class="aside-card">
              <p class="aside-title">mission profile</p>
              <div class="aside-meta">
                <span>Gitea per versionamento e governance del codice.</span>
                <span>n8n per pipeline e automazioni operative.</span>
                <span>Open WebUI + Ollama per modelli locali e interfacce AI.</span>
                <span>Workbench code-server e server PostgreSQL accessibili tramite briefing dedicato.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="aside-card">
              <p class="aside-title">credential policy</p>
              <div class="aside-meta">
                <span>Le credenziali root sono riportate qui e nel file <code>.env</code>.</span>
                <span>n8n usa doppio livello: gateway auth + owner bootstrap al primo ingresso.</span>
                <span>Ollama e esposto come API protetta dal gateway.</span>
                <span>Postgres non ha UI pubblica e viene consumato solo dai workbench.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div>
            <span class="section-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-grid-2"></i> core services</span>
            <h2>Servizi Attivi</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            Ogni card spiega il servizio, mostra le credenziali root e apre direttamente il target
            operativo. Le icone distinguono repository, automazione, interfacce AI e API modelli.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-grid">
          <article class="service-card" data-tilt>
            <div class="service-top">
              <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-code-branch"></i></div>
              <span class="service-status">online</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Gitea Forge</h3>
            <p>
              Repository Git, issue tracking e collaborazione tecnica interna. Punto di ingresso
              per codice, review e governance del progetto.
            </p>
            <div class="credential-grid">
              <div class="credential"><span>Endpoint</span><span>${LAB_EXTERNAL_URL}/lab/dev/gitea/</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Root user</span><span>${GITEA_ROOT_USERNAME}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Password</span><span>${GITEA_ROOT_PASSWORD}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Email</span><span>${GITEA_ROOT_EMAIL}</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-actions">
              <a class="button" href="/lab/dev/gitea/"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> entra</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card" data-tilt>
            <div class="service-top">
              <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-diagram-project"></i></div>
              <span class="service-status">guarded</span>
            </div>
            <h3>n8n Automation</h3>
            <p>
              Motore di workflow e integrazione. Ideale per orchestrare webhook, job, pipeline
              applicative e connessioni tra servizi del lab.
            </p>
            <div class="credential-grid">
              <div class="credential"><span>Endpoint</span><span>${LAB_EXTERNAL_URL}/lab/automation/n8n/</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Gateway user</span><span>${N8N_GATEWAY_USER}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Gateway password</span><span>${N8N_GATEWAY_PASSWORD}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Owner bootstrap</span><span>${N8N_ROOT_FIRST_NAME} ${N8N_ROOT_LAST_NAME}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Owner email</span><span>${N8N_ROOT_EMAIL}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Owner password</span><span>${N8N_ROOT_PASSWORD}</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-actions">
              <a class="button" href="/lab/automation/n8n/"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> entra</a>
            </div>
            <p class="service-note">
              Primo accesso: supera il gateway con le credenziali mostrate sopra e usa le credenziali
              owner per il bootstrap iniziale dell'istanza.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card" data-tilt>
            <div class="service-top">
              <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i></div>
              <span class="service-status">online</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Open WebUI</h3>
            <p>
              Console conversazionale per modelli locali. Espone una UI operativa per usare Ollama,
              testare prompt e gestire flussi AI dal browser.
            </p>
            <div class="credential-grid">
              <div class="credential"><span>Endpoint</span><span>${LAB_EXTERNAL_URL}/lab/ai/open-webui/</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Root name</span><span>${OPENWEBUI_ROOT_NAME}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Root email</span><span>${OPENWEBUI_ROOT_EMAIL}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Password</span><span>${OPENWEBUI_ROOT_PASSWORD}</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-actions">
              <a class="button" href="/lab/ai/open-webui/"><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i> entra</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card" data-tilt>
            <div class="service-top">
              <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i></div>
              <span class="service-status">api</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Ollama Core</h3>
            <p>
              Endpoint locale per inference LLM. Serve i modelli consumati dal lab e puo essere
              interrogato direttamente come API protetta dal gateway.
            </p>
            <div class="credential-grid">
              <div class="credential"><span>Endpoint</span><span>${LAB_EXTERNAL_URL}/lab/ai/ollama/</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Gateway user</span><span>${OLLAMA_GATEWAY_USER}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Gateway password</span><span>${OLLAMA_GATEWAY_PASSWORD}</span></div>
              <div class="credential"><span>Uso</span><span>API locale per modelli</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-actions">
              <a class="button" href="/lab/ai/ollama/"><i class="fa-solid fa-wave-square"></i> apri api</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div>
            <span class="section-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-terminal"></i> development workbenches</span>
            <h2>Ambienti Di Sviluppo</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            Gli ambienti restano operativi ma non vengono linkati come scorciatoie dirette. Dal deck
            apri un briefing markdown locale che spiega cosa fanno, come si accede e quali credenziali usare.
            Postgres resta un nodo infrastrutturale senza UI web, con connessione interna preconfigurata.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="workbench-grid">
          <article class="workbench-card" data-tilt>
            <div class="workbench-top">
              <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-brands fa-node-js"></i></div>
              <span class="service-status">code</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Node Forge</h3>
            <p>Workbench code-server dedicato a JavaScript, TypeScript, frontend e tooling npm, pnpm e yarn.</p>
